column5: CNN, Fox, MSNBC - they're all talking about Joe Daplumma and what he thinks about the US election candidates. I've met Joe on a couple occasions - sure, he's a nice guy, pretty smart, good with the goats etc. but it's getting out of hand!
Hahahaha, I thought the same thing
